      <title>Brookfield 注册一家新的经纪自营商以推动信贷驱动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/brookfield-registers-a-new-broker-dealer-to-fuel-credit-drive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布鲁克菲尔德资产管理公司（Brookfield Asset Management）成立了一家新的美国经纪交易商，这是该公司扩大 3000 亿美元信贷业务计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/brookfield-registers-a-new-broker-dealer-to-fuel-credit-drive</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 18:49:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙击败法国左翼阵营，中间派保留议会最高职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/french-lawmakers-reelect-braun-pivet-head-of-national-assembly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国议员再次选举埃马纽埃尔·马克龙政党的中间派候选人连任国民议会议员，这表明在总统上个月解散立法机构后，总统的联盟可能最有可能组建新政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/french-lawmakers-reelect-braun-pivet-head-of-national-assembly</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 18:46:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德克萨斯州最大的养老基金将从私募股权中撤出近 100 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/texas-teachers-to-pull-almost-10-billion-from-private-equity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州最大的公共养老基金已决定从私募股权投资中撤出近 100 亿美元，这对因回报率减少和投资组合公司退出放缓而面临严格审查的资产类别来说是一个打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/texas-teachers-to-pull-almost-10-billion-from-private-equity</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 18:37:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价企稳，因时差暗示短期供应紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-18</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国原油即期价差扩大且库存连续第三周下降，油价创下一个月来最大单日涨幅，随后保持稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-18</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 23:20:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
